import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-city-page', templateUrl: './city-page.html' }) export class CityPageComp { public forecasts: CityFileStructer = { cityNames: [] } ; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'city/ListCity').subscribe(result => { this.forecasts = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface CityFileStructer { cityNames: Array; }
